      Subclasses of AbstractTargetProcessor in com.fortify.bugtracker.common.tgt.processor 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  AbstractTargetProcessorSubmitIssues
      This abstract IProcessor implementation allows for submitting issues to external systems based on vulnerability data.
      class  AbstractTargetProcessorUpdateIssues
      This abstract IProcessor implementation can update issue state for previously submitted issues, based on possibly updated vulnerability data.
      class  AbstractTargetProcessorUpdateIssuesWithTransitions
      This abstract class extends AbstractTargetProcessorUpdateIssues by adding functionality for transitioning previously submitted issues to a new state.
